properties.Title: Birth of Henry VI
properties.Description: December 6th, 1421: Henry VI is born at Windsor Castle to Catherine of Valois and Henry V.

properties.Title: Death of Henry V
properties.Description: August 31st, 1422: Henry V dies of dysentery at Chateau de Vincennes.

properties.Title: Birth of Margaret of Anjou
properties.Description: March 23rd, 1430: Margaret of Anjou born at Pont-a-Mousson in Loraine.
